#: erpnext/stock/doctype/item_quality_inspection_parameter/item_quality_inspection_parameter.json
#: erpnext/stock/doctype/quality_inspection_reading/quality_inspection_reading.json
msgid ""
"Simple Python formula applied on Reading fields.<br> Numeric eg. 1: "
"<b>reading_1 &gt; 0.2 and reading_1 &lt; 0.5</b><br>\n"
"Numeric eg. 2: <b>mean &gt; 3.5</b> (mean of populated fields)<br>\n"
"Value based eg.:  <b>reading_value in (\"A\", \"B\", \"C\")</b>"
msgstr ""
"صيغة Python بسيطة تطبق على حقول القراءة.<br> رقمي مثال 1: <b>reading_1 > 0.2 "
"and reading_1 < 0.5</b><br>\n"
"رقمي مثال 2: <b>mean > 3.5</b> (متوسط الحقول المملوءة)<br>\n"
"بناءً على القيمة مثال: <b>reading_value in (\"A\", \"B\", \"C\")</b>"

